title: A Greenbriar Christmas Comedy Special With Ti Young Dro Taliban Casino | Ep. 216
itunes:title: A Greenbriar Christmas Comedy Special With Ti Young Dro Taliban Casino | Ep. 216
description:
The coldest podcast brings the funniest comedy show back home. DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean post up at the Woodruff Arts Center in the middle of midtown Atlanta to bring the laughs and they pull up with the day one 85 South Family. Emmanuel Hudson, Navv Greene, Young Dro, T.I. and many more stop thru to represent for the 85 percenters. You already know T.I., Young Dro and Casino crank it up and perform live from the Greenbriar Mall!
